okay..

i feel rather bad right now..i pretty much screwed up alot this week..its amazing how much damage one person can do.
i want to accept people's help..and talk about problems..but i just cant seem to do it.
its like theres a barrier that prevents me from doing it.
maybe its the fact that i feel like ill be judged on everything i say
or people will veiw me diffrently if i tell them whats on my mind
i just want everything to go back to the way it was before..
when i was happy and liked myself..
and when i could tell my best friend whats on my mind
and when guys didnt part people
i dont want morgan to feel shitty on my account.
i dont want her to ruin her friendship with paul
not ever
she is prolly the only person i can really talk to about stuff...
and not feel like she'll hate me
or think im weird
but i dunno
it seems like everything is just...diffrent
not nessisarily between me and her...
well maybe it is
but i dont want it to be
i want us to be like we were at the beggining of all this
when we were open about stuff
and i felt like she totaly got me
y'know

so
this entry is basicly an apology
to morgan
for being there
and trying to help me
it means alot
even though i wasnt open to it
i know you cared...

Thanks
